name: New Born Baby And Mom At Ambulance
name_original: New Born Baby And Mom At Ambulance
description:
"New Born Baby And Mom At Ambulance" is totally free Game.

One day Pregnant Lady going to shopping mall for New Baby's clothes.
She is Fall down on floor. Now She is injured. Need immediate help to lady.
Call Ambulance and Apply treatment in ambulance.

Pregnant Lady Need your Help. Are You Ready to Help Her ?

Specially made for kids.
